<paragraph base="F33206245" id="IFRS09_BC7.64"><paranum>BC7.64</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 9"/><data name="paranum" value="BC7.64"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS09_P7287">Specifically, the IASB amended <xref base="F71918373" href="../ifrs07/IFRS07_42Q.dita#IFRS07_42Q" id="IFRS09_X3240">paragraph 42Q of IFRS 7</xref> to state that an entity need not disclose the line item amounts that would have been reported:</p><ol base="F33206247" id="IFRS09_L0392" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="F33206248" id="IFRS09_P7288">in prior reporting periods in accordance with IFRS 9; or</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="F33206250" id="IFRS09_P7289">in the current reporting period in accordance with <xref base="F71918374" href="../ias39/IAS39_TOC.dita#IAS39_TOC0001/IAS39_TOC0001_V3" id="IFRS09_X3241">IAS 39</xref>.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>